\fBtcpip_tunnel_out_daemon_option()\fR\& = 
.br
    {tcpip_tunnel_out, boolean()}
.br
.fi
.RS
.LP
Enables (\fItrue\fR\&) or disables (\fIfalse\fR\&) the possibility to tunnel a TCP/IP connection out of a server\&. Disabled per default\&.
.RE
